==================================================
GROCERIES OPERATIONAL RULES CONFIRMED

Events controls eligibility.

Groceries controls participation.

---

If Event loses eligibility:

* Status no longer Ordered
  OR
* Active = False

Event is removed from Groceries.

Rebuild rules will apply when downstream grocery data exists.

---

If ToOrder changes:

Event remains in Groceries.

Only downstream participation changes.

